  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The middle child inherited her mother's mind and her father's nerve. Mira's suit, AEGIS-04, is the most experimental of the five — it is also the one that has exploded the most times. She is the Forgeborn's improviser, the one who finds the gap nobody else saw. She has her mother's trust in a way her brother doesn't, which Caden has never fully forgiven.</p>",
